overview: LeaseWithEase empowers tenants to make their own leasing decisions and can save a tenant 10% to 20% on their next lease negotiation. LeaseWithEase is similar to Lending Tree, Travelocity and E*Trade in that we provide free data and tools that were previously only available to the professionals. LeaseWithEase was built for tenants wanting to make their own leasing decision and at no cost to the tenant. Assisting tenants in leasing office, retail and medical office space.
